rmp.university: University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill
comments: Very boring teacher. Be prepared for pop quizzes. The exams are not overly difficult but they are graded harshly and arbitrarily.  Not recommended.
Interesting topics, not too much homework, very straightforward
Not an incredibly exciting lecturer, but the material is very interesting and the class is not overly difficult as long as you read the lecture slides carefully.
